{"title":"一片慈母心","authors":["杨志坚","陈丽君　杨文倩"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":3,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片慈母心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨志坚、陈丽君　作画  杨文倩　配诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗里静悄悄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宝宝睡着了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但闻花儿香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但见蜂儿闹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿姨脚步轻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"床前看宝宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盖上小花被，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把门儿关好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片慈母心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心红手又巧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好比种花人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辛勤来照料。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗里静悄悄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗外春光好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈在田头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又把喜讯报。（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}